snippet.title: Standard Deviation Formula Explained! (TANTON Mathematics)
snippet.description: The formula for standard deviation looks scary and feels scary. Why on earth would anyone want to measure a sense of "spread" of data values with a formula like that??!!!?  Well, let me tell you the very natural and very human story that explains why.
